# MCR-BEV Comparator Configuration
# Copy this file to .mcr-compare.properties and fill in your values.
# Do NOT commit .mcr-compare.properties — it contains secrets.
#
# Resolution order (first found wins):
#   1. CLI arguments (--token, --host, --http-path, --jdbc-url)
#   2. Environment variables (DATABRICKS_TOKEN, DATABRICKS_HOST, DATABRICKS_HTTP_PATH, DATABRICKS_JDBC_URL)
#   3. .mcr-compare.properties in current working directory
#   4. .mcr-compare.properties in user home directory (~/)

